high_descs: Walk forward a half step then turn right to face the stove.
Get the bread out of the microwave and close it.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the bread to the left of the egg on the top shelf and close the door letting it cool down and then get it back out and close the door again.
Walk back to where you got the loaf of bread.
Put it back in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold loaf of bread in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the microwave.
Take the bread out of the microwave.
Head to the right and back to the fridge.
Chill the bread in the fridge.
Bring the bread back to the microwave on the left.
Put the bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the stove.
Open the microwave and take out the object inside. Shut the door.
Take the bread and turn around and find the fridge on the left.
Open the fridge and put the bread inside. Shut the door. Open the fridge, take the break out and shut the door.
Take the bread, turn around then make a right to go back to the stove.
Place the bread in the microwave.
